{"tid":2205775,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 發售資訊公佈：售價 US$400 起，11 月 12 日起在部分地區上市","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:51:47.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96bf929cfbc3bff88e3dd408145e71aa933b3ced","tid":2205775,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"無光碟機的數位版價格是 US$400，有光碟機的標準版要價 US$500，中港台三地均未出現在第一批發售地區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/d7fa5ec0-f860-11ea-b9df-3c1bf5e16f3a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2Fd7fa5ec0-f860-11ea-b9df-3c1bf5e16f3a&h=b7b4a3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊跟著對手 Xbox Series X 和 S，在今天 Sony 舉辦的遊戲介紹活動中，PlayStation 5 系列的發售資訊也終於公開了。最終標準版和數位版 PS5 的價格分別是 US$500（約 HK$3,880 / NT$14,620）和 US$400（約 HK$3,100 / NT$11,700），兩者均會從 11 月 12 日起率先在日本、美國、加拿大、墨西哥、澳洲、紐西蘭和南韓上市，全球其它地區的發售日期則為 11 月 19 日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/d8532d20-f860-11ea-bf7f-957679165cc7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2Fd8532d20-f860-11ea-bf7f-957679165cc7&h=325e4a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣一來，還在考慮次世代主機選哪家的玩家至少在價格上已經可以有一個判斷。微軟和 Sony 這次的當家產品在售價上打了個平手，但在數位版的較量中，Xbox Series S 的價格要便宜 US$100 之多（約 HK$780 / NT$2,920）。而在發售日期確定以後，相信接下來各家遊戲廠商也會陸續公佈次世代新作的上架時間了吧。<br />\n<br />\n更新：Sony 後續也一併公佈了各類配件的價格。DualSense 手把的價格為 US$70（約 HK$540 / NT$2,050），雙手把充電底座的價格是 US$30（約 HK$230 / NT$880），HD Camera 相機售價 US$60（約 HK$470 / NT$1,750），Pulse 3D 耳機賣 US$100（約 HK$780 / NT$2,920），PS5 媒體遙控器要是 US$30（約 HK$230 / NT$880）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/ps5-price-release-date-211056700.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fps5-price-release-date-211056700.html&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bjr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=3272fd8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/ps5-price-release-date-211056700.html</a>"},{"pid":"a529fbaca9174ecb1a060af22d6c9b87271fe29b","tid":2205775,"uid":16745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"頭先amazon preorder 咗光碟版<br />\n希望準時收貨"},{"pid":"56091aa69ef8a6cca6a1ea89a9e748d7b7a1798d","tid":2205775,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b9005d40d7f5fd20a68ea51a435ef766b1f2fdf","tid":2205775,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a529fbaca9174ecb1a060af22d6c9b87271fe29b","tid":2205775,"uid":16745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"頭先amazon preorder 咗光碟版<br />\n希望準時收貨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"集運搵間快嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排成日遲到港"},{"pid":"e09b8bb96dd89523df985e2793cdb58b3416d367","tid":2205775,"uid":274725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"56091aa69ef8a6cca6a1ea89a9e748d7b7a1798d","tid":2205775,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔識睇內文？"},{"pid":"abe9ff6e9af0efcb253d11d61a846293a122c30e","tid":2205775,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09b8bb96dd89523df985e2793cdb58b3416d367","tid":2205775,"uid":274725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"56091aa69ef8a6cca6a1ea89a9e748d7b7a1798d","tid":2205775,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔識睇內文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbff8531747c2fc3df00473